    <item>
      <title>印尼工商领袖称，印尼必须改革才能实现 8% 的 GDP 增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/indonesia-must-reform-to-hit-8-gdp-growth-business-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位颇具影响力的商业协会领导人表示，如果印尼想要实现新总统普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 提出的国内生产总值年增长率 8% 的目标，就需要改革国有企业并增加投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/indonesia-must-reform-to-hit-8-gdp-growth-business-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 07:30:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刺激计划疑虑令多头望而却步，中国股市暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/chinese-stocks-slump-amid-stimulus-skepticism-weak-holiday-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员对北京方面刺激措施的步伐感到不耐烦，且疲软的假日消费数据打击了市场人气，中国在岸上市的股票遭遇了四年多来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/chinese-stocks-slump-amid-stimulus-skepticism-weak-holiday-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 01:35:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
